# vul-agent overview

- vul-agent implements a trustworthy and precise vulnerability detection AI agent that discovers software vulnerabilities and validate them by testing exploitation.

The project is structured as

```bash
vulagent/__init__  # Protocols/interfaces for all base classes
vulagent/agents  # Agent control flow & loop
vulagent/environments  # Executing agent actions
vulagent/models  # LM interfaces
vulagent/run  # Run scripts that serve as an entry point
```

- The project embraces polymorphism: Every individual class should be simple, but we offer alternatives
- Every use case should start with a run script, that picks one agent, environment, and model class to run